trailingComments.value:
Solve Q + t * D = b1 * E1 + b2 * E2
		 * (Q = kDiff, D = ray direction, E1 = kEdge1, E2 = kEdge2,
		 * N = Cross(E1, E2)):
		 *
		 *   | Dot(D, N) | * b1 = sign(Dot(D, N)) * Dot(D, Cross(Q, E2))
		 *   | Dot(D, N) | * b2 = sign(Dot(D, N)) * Dot(D, Cross(E1, Q))
		 *   | Dot(D, N) | * t = -sign(Dot(D, N)) * Dot(Q, N)
